Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.11,0:01:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加州理工学院天文学家麦克·布朗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Caltech astronomer, Mike Brown
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.01,0:01:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过调动一连串事件 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Set in motion a chain of events That reduced
