Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.99,0:02:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九大行星中冥王星是唯一的一颗的冰球体 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There was no way That Pluto could survive the its status
