Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.79,0:32:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海王星名字取自罗马的海神 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Neptune takes its name From the Roman god of the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.47,0:32:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海王星离地球26.8亿英里远 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Neptune is 2.68 billion miles From Earth.
