Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.65,0:32:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海王星上一年等于地球上的165年 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A year on Neptune is equivalent To 165 Earth years,
