Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.97,0:32:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要属海王星 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Are on Neptune.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.05,0:32:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海王星的风有时每小时1千多英里 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We have winds of sometimes Over 1,000 miles per hour
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.35,0:33:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上层大气的风一般有750英里每小时 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And commonly, 750 miles per hour Raging in that upper atmosphere.
