Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.82,0:33:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究其他行星上影响气候的驱动力 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Studies what drives weather On other planets.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.42,0:33:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海王星上神秘的强风激起了他的兴趣 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He's intrigued by Neptune's Mysteriously strong winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.03,0:33:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们把这些风车放到海王星上面去 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If we were to put One of these windmills Up on Neptune
