Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.27,0:33:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们实际上看不到风车这样的转动 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We actually might not see Very much motion at all,
