Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.28,0:34:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是加热空气的热能源 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Is an energy source To heat the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.25,0:34:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球上 太阳提供了这一热能源 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}On Earth, The sun provides this energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.86,0:34:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这颗刮风的海王星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But the windswept planet Neptune
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.56,0:34:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与太阳的距离比地球要远30倍 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Is 30 times farther from the sun Than Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.56,0:34:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到的太阳能也只有地球的1/900 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And it gets only about 1/900th As much solar energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.10,0:34:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点能量显然不足以产生海王星上的狂风 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's simply not enough To power Neptune's Colossal winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.07,0:35:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科学家认为海王星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Scientists believe that neptune
