Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.95,0:35:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航天器2号的数据测试显示 海王星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Measurements taken by Voyager II Showed that Neptune
