Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.43,0:35:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海王星的内热相对较多 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Neptune has A relatively large amount Of internal heating
