Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.61,0:35:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些衰变和化学过程就释放了许多热量 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And that releases a lot of heat From the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.01,0:35:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是为什么海王星内部\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Just why The interior of Neptune
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.78,0:35:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能产生如此多的能量这还是个秘 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Generates so much heat Remains a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.79,0:35:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的人推测\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's lead some to speculate
