Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.54,0:36:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大气中有许多明亮白色的云层出现 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There are many bright, White clouds that appear In the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.95,0:36:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明暗不同的区域镶嵌在海王星表层 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There are different regions Of very bright and dark banding On the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.22,0:36:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们能够区分出不同的纬度 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So we'd be able to distinguish Different latitudes
